  "detailed_description": "AviGames presents the seventh game in the hidden object series of \"Big Adventure: Trip to Europe\". Embark on a journey through beautiful European countries and look for hidden objects in old Europe and Scandinavia, play exciting mini-games and collect souvenirs from different countries.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis wonderful journey will take you through many tourist destinations in various European countries. You will enjoy visiting several national parks, exploring European musical culture, ancient castles and much more. This hidden object game is full of new and popular tourist spots. Use your skills and knowledge to play mini-games and find all the hidden objects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe collector's edition includes:<br />\r\n- 10 additional locations - find even more objects and a funny raccoon! <br />\r\n- 5 additional new mini-games + 12 more for puzzle lovers <br />\r\n- Beautiful desktop wallpapers <br />\r\n- Music player <br />\r\n- A collection of unique souvenirs <br />\r\n- 20 great souvenirs from the journey",
  "about_the_game": "AviGames presents the seventh game in the hidden object series of \"Big Adventure: Trip to Europe\". Embark on a journey through beautiful European countries and look for hidden objects in old Europe and Scandinavia, play exciting mini-games and collect souvenirs from different countries.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis wonderful journey will take you through many tourist destinations in various European countries. You will enjoy visiting several national parks, exploring European musical culture, ancient castles and much more. This hidden object game is full of new and popular tourist spots. Use your skills and knowledge to play mini-games and find all the hidden objects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe collector's edition includes:<br />\r\n- 10 additional locations - find even more objects and a funny raccoon! <br />\r\n- 5 additional new mini-games + 12 more for puzzle lovers <br />\r\n- Beautiful desktop wallpapers <br />\r\n- Music player <br />\r\n- A collection of unique souvenirs <br />\r\n- 20 great souvenirs from the journey",
